The paper presents a new algorithm for learning continuous motor skills directly from raw visual input, which involves deep learning, robotics, computer vision, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
